title: The Best bits of the Late Show
creator_credit: D Generation, ABC-TV (Australia), Michael Hirsch, Mark Gibson and Joe Murray
brief_description: Here is your chance to be treated to some ‘Champagne comedy’ from the D-Generation team’s crowning Glory - The Late Show. Re-live these classic moments; Shitscared, Graham and the Colonel, Pissweak World, Ouchy Wouchy Heart, The Mr. Whippy Grand Prix, Things wogs won’t do, plus literally dozens more sketches. You’ll laugh ‘til you cry!
